ISLAMABAD, Nov 19 (APP): Foreign Minister Shah Mahmood Qureshi Thursday expressed grief over the demise of chief of Tehreek-i-Labbaik Pakistan Maulana Khadim Rizvi who breathed his last a while ago.
The foreign minister prayed for peace of the departed soul and strength to the family members and followers to bear the loss with equanimity, a foreign ministry press release said.
